column5: Sometimes at school, I refer to myself as an alien from Mars, and they start making jokes about how they come from the sun and the other planets. I say I want to return to my planet as I was sent here to learn about humans and they just laughed not thinking of it. They just don't realize I want to die and "return to my own planet."
I thought i could be away from my family for a while if i stay in hospital

Sometimes i just feel like, I wanna die

But then I realised

I can't be able to read those cheesy fanfictions on wattpad anymore

I can't watch any animes anymore

I can't see my favourite bands sing live anymore

Then i wait

I'd probs listen to all the songs of one direction or 5sos

cuz i dont really have a fav
